description:
On this week's episode, Jojo Zarur from Love and Hip Hop Miami sits with the ladies of Lip Service and things get messy. Jojo admits to doing full background checks before dating someone. Lore'l confesses to a sexual act that no one else in the room has done before, and Gigi remembers some crazy fetishes she's encountered in the past. The ladies discuss mixing business with pleasure, being betrayed by "friends," and much more! They even try to help a fellow Lip Service listener with his small penis problems
